          <h4>Be Discovered</h4>
            <h6>Kids2ProSports.com – Your Introduction to the World of Sports Recognition</h6>
            <p>K2PS is a virtual global networking community designed to provide a variety of services to educate, support, and nurture athletes of all ages.</p>
            <p>We all have experienced, spending countless hours and money providing the fundamental tools that we believe our children need to succeed in their sports career. K2PS was developed based on the belief that everyone should have an equal opportunity by offering the tools to take those efforts to the next level; to help gain a local2global audience to showcase and compare our member's sport skills and create unlimited sport, educational and professional opportunities.</p>
            <p>There is an expression "The World Is Your Stage",but not if no one knows about you. <p>
            <p>In our 24-hour sport news cycle, reputation and image is an important aspect of an athlete's success, K2PS was developed to give athletes the opportunity to proactively manage their image and to assist in their athletic branding in the sport landscape.</p>
            <p>K2PS provides the most comprehensive source for industry connections, featuring 360 social network options; 75 national & international sport groups with over 1.3 million members and support of over 10 million associates; organizations whose memberships represent over 80 million athletes; thousands of college coaches and millions of sport enthusiasts and sport related professionals. </p>
            <p>The United States is a melting pot of cultures from around the world, and the sports its athletes participate in reflect that variety.</p>
            <p>Through this cross-generational Sport Legacy Search Engine, athletes can create a personal game plan specific to their vision for personal achievement, broadening their appeal on the road to success and increased opportunities as a public sports figure, balancing academic excellence and sports participation. </p>
            <div class="para">
              <h6>Some Facts:</h6>
              The current US population is almost 310.6 million and 90% of the youth in the USA participate in some form of sport activity.<br />
              There are 23.6 million people in the United States who play some form of professional sports.
              The National Council of Youth Sports membership has over 44 million boys & girls who are participating in youth sports and 60 million members overall.<br />
              Gatorade's research indicates there are 68 million performance athletes and 55 million fitness athletes.<br />
              There are 7 billion human being and over 2.3 billion participate in some form of sport activity.
              Baby boomers (ages 50 – 74) are a generation of 78 million strong and their interest is an active lifestyle in sports and fitness.*<br />
              
              *To view the resources for these facts visit <a href="#">Internet Sports Marketing "News"</a>
          </div>
          <div>
              <b>You need a competitive advantage.</b> We are here for you…..join our sports community and let us introduce you the world of sports recognition, competition and connections.
              <p>For a personal analysis of your goals and how we may help, please contact us at <a href="#">BeDiscovered@K2ps.com.</a></p>
